summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds to a portion of the southeast one-quarter of Section 30, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; a portion of Blocks 1 and 2, Lusk Heights; a portion of Block 5, Lindsley's Mineral Springs Plat; and a portion of the southwest one-quarter of Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., for street purposes and laying off Meridian Avenue North and North Northgate Way. (North Northgate Way, Widening)
